OOC: Well ok this is gonna be wierd ill do this just to end this crappy 
battle that way we can regroup once this whole thing gets straightened out 
and we can try this again.
 Hydras took shots from all sides. Fire spilled out and he yelped in pain. He 
had to retreat he knew it. This battle was over, and he was picking up a new 
ship orbiting the moon. These new devolpments would become interesting. 
"Predacons retreat!" He turned and fired as many shots as he could floating 
upward and flying off towards his base. Proto followed him try to give him 
some cover fire.

--part1_14d.1775a86a.2b085c61_boundary
